  <article class="article">
    <h2>Welcome to Healthy Living!</h2>
    <p>
      Health is a state of complete physical, mental, and social well-being. Here, we share tips and advice on how to maintain a balanced lifestyle. Let's dive in!
    </p>
    <h3>Nutrition</h3>
    <p>
      Eating a balanced diet is key to good health. A healthy diet includes a variety of fruits and vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins, and healthy fats.
    </p>
    <h3>Exercise</h3>
    <p>
      Regular physical activity can improve your muscle strength and boost your endurance. Exercise delivers oxygen and nutrients to your tissues and helps your cardiovascular system work more efficiently.
    </p>
    <h3>Mental Health</h3>
    <p>
      Mental health is as important as physical health. It's crucial to take time out for yourself, connect with others, stay positive, and get plenty of sleep.
    </p>
